# bgp-vpn-1 decoding test - VPNv4 NLRI via ze-test decode
# Tests VPNv4 route with RD 0:1:1, label 100, prefix 10.0.0.0/24
#
# Wire bytes breakdown:
# 70 = 112 bits total (24 label + 64 RD + 24 prefix)
# 00 06 41 = MPLS label 100 with S-bit
# 00 00 00 01 00 00 00 01 = RD type 0: ASN=1, value=1
# 0a 00 00 = 10.0.0.0/24
stdin=payload:hex=7000064100000001000000010a0000
cmd=foreground:seq=1:exec=ze-test decode --json --nlri ipv4/mpls-vpn -:stdin=payload
expect=json:json={ "labels": [[100]], "prefix": "10.0.0.0/24", "rd": "0:1:1" }
